Text.SourceString: You must be <PlayerName>$player</>, right?//<portrait=normal>Damn, I wasn’t expecting you to look like <Italic>this</>.//You’re surprisingly cute!
Text.LocalizedString: You must be <PlayerName>$player</>, right?//<portrait=normal>Damn, I wasn’t expecting you to look like <Italic>this</>.//You’re surprisingly cute!

Text.SourceString: Well, it’s nice to finally meet you! Name’s <NPCName>Pablo</>.//I don’t know jack about farming, but hey!//<portrait=happy>If you need help with tools, come by my shop just north of town, and I’ll see what I can do. Ciao!
Text.LocalizedString: Well, it’s nice to finally meet you! Name’s <NPCName>Pablo</>.//I don’t know jack about farming, but hey!//<portrait=happy>If you need help with tools, come by my shop just north of town, and I’ll see what I can do. Ciao!

Text.SourceString: It’s important to have a hobby.//Gives you a chance to really dig deep into who you are.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s important to have a hobby.//Gives you a chance to really dig deep into who you are.

Text.SourceString: It's the small stuff, like how we entertain ourselves…//They’re what makes us who we are, eh?
Text.LocalizedString: It's the small stuff, like how we entertain ourselves…//They’re what makes us who we are, eh?

Text.SourceString: I try to see my friends after work most days.//Just to take the edge off.
Text.LocalizedString: I try to see my friends after work most days.//Just to take the edge off.

Text.SourceString: But if I’m too tired, I’ll just chill in the garage and tinker with my speakers.//<portrait=happy>No big deal.
Text.LocalizedString: But if I’m too tired, I’ll just chill in the garage and tinker with my speakers.//<portrait=happy>No big deal.

Text.SourceString: We develop new weapons every now and then.//Well, basically whenever we have the time, to be honest.
Text.LocalizedString: We develop new weapons every now and then.//Well, basically whenever we have the time, to be honest.

Text.SourceString: Don’t worry about our weapons breaking in the middle of combat.//They're built to last!
Text.LocalizedString: Don’t worry about our weapons breaking in the middle of combat.//They're built to last!

Text.SourceString: I usually take two days to upgrade tools, so please plan accordingly if you want something worked on.
Text.LocalizedString: I usually take two days to upgrade tools, so please plan accordingly if you want something worked on.

Text.SourceString: Throwing extra coins at me won't speed up the process...yeah, I know.
Text.LocalizedString: Throwing extra coins at me won't speed up the process...yeah, I know.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Ben’s</> the man if you want a fresh perspective.//I like to get his opinion when I’ve got a tough decision to make.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Ben’s</> the man if you want a fresh perspective.//I like to get his opinion when I’ve got a tough decision to make.

Text.SourceString: He's got a unique vibe going on. Cool guy.
Text.LocalizedString: He's got a unique vibe going on. Cool guy.

Text.SourceString: Did you know <NPCName>Frank</> hates yogurt?//<portrait=normal>A weird thing to hate, isn’t it?
Text.LocalizedString: Did you know <NPCName>Frank</> hates yogurt?//<portrait=normal>A weird thing to hate, isn’t it?

Text.SourceString: He also hates durian, but that, I get.//<portrait=concerned>I wouldn't touch a durian with a ten-metre pole.
Text.LocalizedString: He also hates durian, but that, I get.//<portrait=concerned>I wouldn't touch a durian with a ten-metre pole.

Text.SourceString: Business hours, huh? You're making it sound so official, <PlayerName>$player</>. Ha!//<portrait=normal>Our shop is open Monday to Saturday. We’re closed on Sunday.
Text.LocalizedString: Business hours, huh? You're making it sound so official, <PlayerName>$player</>. Ha!//<portrait=normal>Our shop is open Monday to Saturday. We’re closed on Sunday.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Rafael</> wants a day off to spend time with the rest of the family, so we decided to close the shop on Sundays.//He’s usually gone all day.//<portrait=normal>It gives me time to relax.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Rafael</> wants a day off to spend time with the rest of the family, so we decided to close the shop on Sundays.//He’s usually gone all day.//<portrait=normal>It gives me time to relax.

Text.SourceString: We close early on Saturdays.//<portrait=normal>So, if you need my help, better ask before noon.
Text.LocalizedString: We close early on Saturdays.//<portrait=normal>So, if you need my help, better ask before noon.

Text.SourceString: My free time? Hmm…//I usually head to town and run some errands.//If not that, I’ll probably just be hanging out at the Tavern.
Text.LocalizedString: My free time? Hmm…//I usually head to town and run some errands.//If not that, I’ll probably just be hanging out at the Tavern.

Text.SourceString: Having a good day so far?
Text.LocalizedString: Having a good day so far?

Text.SourceString: My cousin <NPCName>Antonio</>, <NPCName>Valentina’s</> dad, comes here for festivals sometimes.
Text.LocalizedString: My cousin <NPCName>Antonio</>, <NPCName>Valentina’s</> dad, comes here for festivals sometimes.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Valentina</>. Errr…<NPCName>Suki’s</> daughter.//Ring a bell?
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Valentina</>. Errr…<NPCName>Suki’s</> daughter.//Ring a bell?

Text.SourceString: You look like you had a good day!
Text.LocalizedString: You look like you had a good day!

Text.SourceString: Any plans for the weekend?
Text.LocalizedString: Any plans for the weekend?

Text.SourceString: I dropped some eggs today trying to make breakfast. Such a waste of food.
Text.LocalizedString: I dropped some eggs today trying to make breakfast. Such a waste of food.

Text.SourceString: When it comes to birthdays, people mostly just appreciate you remembering. Kinda shows they're in your thoughts.
Text.LocalizedString: When it comes to birthdays, people mostly just appreciate you remembering. Kinda shows they're in your thoughts.

Text.SourceString: But hey, gifts never hurt either!
Text.LocalizedString: But hey, gifts never hurt either!

Text.SourceString: Yeah, I'm a bit of a Tavern regular. You noticed, huh?//<portrait=normal>Could be after work or on the weekend. Whenever I'm feeling it.
Text.LocalizedString: Yeah, I'm a bit of a Tavern regular. You noticed, huh?//<portrait=normal>Could be after work or on the weekend. Whenever I'm feeling it.

Text.SourceString: Good food, great crowd. What else could I ask for, right?
Text.LocalizedString: Good food, great crowd. What else could I ask for, right?

Text.SourceString: Your tools holding up all right, <PlayerName>$player</>?
Text.LocalizedString: Your tools holding up all right, <PlayerName>$player</>?

Text.SourceString: Bring 'em by if they need some work, okay? I'll see what I can do.
Text.LocalizedString: Bring 'em by if they need some work, okay? I'll see what I can do.

Text.SourceString: I keep forgetting to read this book my brother got me about legendary blacksmiths.
Text.LocalizedString: I keep forgetting to read this book my brother got me about legendary blacksmiths.

Text.SourceString: Maybe tonight I'll finally sit down and read the darn thing.
Text.LocalizedString: Maybe tonight I'll finally sit down and read the darn thing.

Text.SourceString: It’s <Italic>finally</> getting warmer. Can't wait to get back outside.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s <Italic>finally</> getting warmer. Can't wait to get back outside.

Text.SourceString: The Cherry Blossom Festival is out of this world.//<portrait=happy>Good people, great food, what's better than that?
Text.LocalizedString: The Cherry Blossom Festival is out of this world.//<portrait=happy>Good people, great food, what's better than that?

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Charles</> was sneezing all night when I saw him at the Tavern. Poor guy.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Charles</> was sneezing all night when I saw him at the Tavern. Poor guy.

Text.SourceString: Workshop's not too hot right now. Kinda nice and warm, really.
Text.LocalizedString: Workshop's not too hot right now. Kinda nice and warm, really.

Text.SourceString: Spring always brings so much life. Kinda makes me feel more alive too.
Text.LocalizedString: Spring always brings so much life. Kinda makes me feel more alive too.

Text.SourceString: <Italic>Gah</>, I love Summer! Everyone's out and about, having a good time.//<portrait=blushing>And I gotta say, I think I look pretty good in Summer clothes. What do you think?
Text.LocalizedString: <Italic>Gah</>, I love Summer! Everyone's out and about, having a good time.//<portrait=blushing>And I gotta say, I think I look pretty good in Summer clothes. What do you think?

Text.SourceString: I was reminded yesterday how I hate working in front of the furnace in Summer. I bet you never felt heat like the heat of a furnace on a hot Summer day.
Text.LocalizedString: I was reminded yesterday how I hate working in front of the furnace in Summer. I bet you never felt heat like the heat of a furnace on a hot Summer day.

Text.SourceString: How can I work inside on such a beautiful day?//<portrait=sad>Sometimes being a blacksmith sucks.
Text.LocalizedString: How can I work inside on such a beautiful day?//<portrait=sad>Sometimes being a blacksmith sucks.

Text.SourceString: I'm not even exaggerating when I say the Beach Cleanup Festival is my favorite. Love seeing the community come together like that.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm not even exaggerating when I say the Beach Cleanup Festival is my favorite. Love seeing the community come together like that.

Text.SourceString: The trash collecting isn’t a contest per se, but…//<portrait=blushing>I like to think it is.
Text.LocalizedString: The trash collecting isn’t a contest per se, but…//<portrait=blushing>I like to think it is.

Text.SourceString: Can't figure out why my little bro keeps staying inside. Doesn't he get that Summer is the best time to be out and about?
Text.LocalizedString: Can't figure out why my little bro keeps staying inside. Doesn't he get that Summer is the best time to be out and about?

Text.SourceString: So glad it's starting to cool down. Makes working at the shop a lot easier.
Text.LocalizedString: So glad it's starting to cool down. Makes working at the shop a lot easier.

Text.SourceString: I can’t wait for the Harvest Festival. I wonder what everyone is going to show.
Text.LocalizedString: I can’t wait for the Harvest Festival. I wonder what everyone is going to show.

Text.SourceString: Now Fall is here, that farm must be working you hard, huh? The season of harvest and all…//I can tell. Farming looks good on you.
Text.LocalizedString: Now Fall is here, that farm must be working you hard, huh? The season of harvest and all…//I can tell. Farming looks good on you.

Text.SourceString: Our family has been helping out Starlet Town by setting up festivals and putting up seasonal decorations.//Gotta admit, the Fall festival decorations are some of my faves.
Text.LocalizedString: Our family has been helping out Starlet Town by setting up festivals and putting up seasonal decorations.//Gotta admit, the Fall festival decorations are some of my faves.

Text.SourceString: I've been thinking about heading over to the hot spring one of these days… Clear out some leaves for <NPCName>Takeba</>.
Text.LocalizedString: I've been thinking about heading over to the hot spring one of these days… Clear out some leaves for <NPCName>Takeba</>.

Text.SourceString: It’s starting to get too cold for my taste. I’m not looking forward to Winter…//A hot spring does sound pretty sweet right about now, huh?
Text.LocalizedString: It’s starting to get too cold for my taste. I’m not looking forward to Winter…//A hot spring does sound pretty sweet right about now, huh?

Text.SourceString: Winter is such a bummer.//I can’t stand being outdoors in the cold too long.
Text.LocalizedString: Winter is such a bummer.//I can’t stand being outdoors in the cold too long.

Text.SourceString: You know what? Sometimes Winter isn’t so bad. At the very least, it makes working in front of the furnace so much better.//<portrait=sad>I’d still rather be outside, though…
Text.LocalizedString: You know what? Sometimes Winter isn’t so bad. At the very least, it makes working in front of the furnace so much better.//<portrait=sad>I’d still rather be outside, though…

Text.SourceString: On one hand, I get so bored cooped up inside. On the other hand, it’s so dang cold out!//<portrait=sad>What should I do?
Text.LocalizedString: On one hand, I get so bored cooped up inside. On the other hand, it’s so dang cold out!//<portrait=sad>What should I do?

Text.SourceString: Might ask my little brother to go to the hot spring with me next week.//I don’t like him being all alone <Italic>all</> the time.
Text.LocalizedString: Might ask my little brother to go to the hot spring with me next week.//I don’t like him being all alone <Italic>all</> the time.

Text.SourceString: The furnace can keep the whole house warm, all right…//We don't really need an extra heater.
Text.LocalizedString: The furnace can keep the whole house warm, all right…//We don't really need an extra heater.

Text.SourceString: My little brother and I used to play in the snow until late. When we were kids, of course.//We’d make sleighs from tree trunks and just go sliding back and forth.
Text.LocalizedString: My little brother and I used to play in the snow until late. When we were kids, of course.//We’d make sleighs from tree trunks and just go sliding back and forth.

Text.SourceString: So what do you think of the Winter decorations, <PlayerName>$player</>? <NPCName>Rafael</> and I put them up every year.//They’re great, right? Makes the town more festive.
Text.LocalizedString: So what do you think of the Winter decorations, <PlayerName>$player</>? <NPCName>Rafael</> and I put them up every year.//They’re great, right? Makes the town more festive.

Text.SourceString: It doesn’t really feel like Winter until I see the festive Winter decorations.
Text.LocalizedString: It doesn’t really feel like Winter until I see the festive Winter decorations.

Text.SourceString: I'm pretty much over Winter. Can't wait for Spring to roll in.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm pretty much over Winter. Can't wait for Spring to roll in.

Text.SourceString: The drilling company?//<portrait=angry>Yeah… Everyone’s talking about it.
Text.LocalizedString: The drilling company?//<portrait=angry>Yeah… Everyone’s talking about it.

Text.SourceString: How was your first festival? I hope you finally got to meet everyone.
Text.LocalizedString: How was your first festival? I hope you finally got to meet everyone.

Text.SourceString: School’s important. I’m glad we get to keep the school going on such a small island.
Text.LocalizedString: School’s important. I’m glad we get to keep the school going on such a small island.

Text.SourceString: Had a chat with <NpcName>Randy</> about it, and keeping the education budget afloat is no picnic.
Text.LocalizedString: Had a chat with <NpcName>Randy</> about it, and keeping the education budget afloat is no picnic.

Text.SourceString: I’m trying to persuade my cousins to expand the inn’s business.//Maybe they could add karaoke! Let people choose songs and sing along.//<portrait=sad>They keep turning me down.//Didn’t see the potential, I guess.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m trying to persuade my cousins to expand the inn’s business.//Maybe they could add karaoke! Let people choose songs and sing along.//<portrait=sad>They keep turning me down.//Didn’t see the potential, I guess.

Text.SourceString: My cousins? Well, technically, the twins who run the inn are my ex-cousins-in-law, but we just treat them like family.//Thought that was pretty standard, but maybe it's just an us thing…
Text.LocalizedString: My cousins? Well, technically, the twins who run the inn are my ex-cousins-in-law, but we just treat them like family.//Thought that was pretty standard, but maybe it's just an us thing…

Text.SourceString: Any big plans for the Summer?
Text.LocalizedString: Any big plans for the Summer?

Text.SourceString: I'll probably just chill at the Tavern and work on my speakers, same old, same old.
Text.LocalizedString: I'll probably just chill at the Tavern and work on my speakers, same old, same old.

Text.SourceString: Ugh, today’s a busy day for me. I could use a cold drink right about now.
Text.LocalizedString: Ugh, today’s a busy day for me. I could use a cold drink right about now.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Rafael</> and I went over to the inn and had a quick dinner with our niece, <NPCName>Valentina</>, to celebrate her birthday last week.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Rafael</> and I went over to the inn and had a quick dinner with our niece, <NPCName>Valentina</>, to celebrate her birthday last week.

Text.SourceString: I gave her a geode... Thought she'd get a kick out of a geode, hunting for treasures and all, but I guess I missed the mark…
Text.LocalizedString: I gave her a geode... Thought she'd get a kick out of a geode, hunting for treasures and all, but I guess I missed the mark…

Text.SourceString: The annual beach cleanup's taking place near the inn, and I'm sure everyone's gonna chip in.
Text.LocalizedString: The annual beach cleanup's taking place near the inn, and I'm sure everyone's gonna chip in.

Text.SourceString: Any reason is a good reason to get together, eh, <PlayerName>$player</>?
Text.LocalizedString: Any reason is a good reason to get together, eh, <PlayerName>$player</>?

Text.SourceString: Fall is here, and I haven’t gotten anything for <NPCName>Rafael’s</> birthday yet…
Text.LocalizedString: Fall is here, and I haven’t gotten anything for <NPCName>Rafael’s</> birthday yet…

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Rafael</> loves onyx. I sure hope <NPCName>Ben</> has some in stock right now, or else I don’t know what to do.//<portrait=concerned>Do you know where I can get an onyx? Just in case <NPCName>Ben</> doesn’t have any.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Rafael</> loves onyx. I sure hope <NPCName>Ben</> has some in stock right now, or else I don’t know what to do.//<portrait=concerned>Do you know where I can get an onyx? Just in case <NPCName>Ben</> doesn’t have any.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Rafael</> loves onyx. <NPCName>Ben</> is usually my go-to guy for rare items, but he’s out of town. That’s just great… Do you know where I can get an onyx?
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Rafael</> loves onyx. <NPCName>Ben</> is usually my go-to guy for rare items, but he’s out of town. That’s just great… Do you know where I can get an onyx?

Text.SourceString: For<NPCName>Rafael’s</> birthday last week, I gave him some cake from the Tavern. He seemed to like it.
Text.LocalizedString: For<NPCName>Rafael’s</> birthday last week, I gave him some cake from the Tavern. He seemed to like it.

Text.SourceString: Next Summer, I’m going to remind myself to set aside one piece of onyx for his birthday. Because I know <NPCName>Rafael</> loves that stuff.
Text.LocalizedString: Next Summer, I’m going to remind myself to set aside one piece of onyx for his birthday. Because I know <NPCName>Rafael</> loves that stuff.

Text.SourceString: The last day of Fall is the busiest day for us.//That’s when <NPCName>Rafael</> and I put up Winter decorations around town. You know, so it looks more festive! Adds a little color to the plain white snow.
Text.LocalizedString: The last day of Fall is the busiest day for us.//That’s when <NPCName>Rafael</> and I put up Winter decorations around town. You know, so it looks more festive! Adds a little color to the plain white snow.

Text.SourceString: Have you gotten the greenhouse fixed up? You can plant a bunch of different stuff in there all year round.
Text.LocalizedString: Have you gotten the greenhouse fixed up? You can plant a bunch of different stuff in there all year round.

Text.SourceString: Are you planting anything in your greenhouse this Winter?
Text.LocalizedString: Are you planting anything in your greenhouse this Winter?

Text.SourceString: I’m sure you already know this, but plants in the greenhouse don’t wither. Easy income all year round, eh?
Text.LocalizedString: I’m sure you already know this, but plants in the greenhouse don’t wither. Easy income all year round, eh?

Text.SourceString: I’m sure you already know this, but plants don’t wither inside the greenhouse. Easy income all year round, eh?
Text.LocalizedString: I’m sure you already know this, but plants don’t wither inside the greenhouse. Easy income all year round, eh?

Text.SourceString: I’m cold. Why does it have to be this cold?
Text.LocalizedString: I’m cold. Why does it have to be this cold?

Text.SourceString: *shivers*
Text.LocalizedString: *shivers*

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Ben</>'s got a friend who's a miner. Sometimes I have her score me some rare ore, like osmium, trading it for gold plates or weapons.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Ben</>'s got a friend who's a miner. Sometimes I have her score me some rare ore, like osmium, trading it for gold plates or weapons.

Text.SourceString: It can get pretty boring being indoors all day.
Text.LocalizedString: It can get pretty boring being indoors all day.

Text.SourceString: With this cold, there's hardly anyone out and about.
Text.LocalizedString: With this cold, there's hardly anyone out and about.

Text.SourceString: I try to catch up with my niece and cousins when I can.//<NPCName>Rafael</> and I have this ongoing bet about who's the better uncle to <NPCName>Valentina</>.//<portrait=blushing>Who do you think is ahead?
Text.LocalizedString: I try to catch up with my niece and cousins when I can.//<NPCName>Rafael</> and I have this ongoing bet about who's the better uncle to <NPCName>Valentina</>.//<portrait=blushing>Who do you think is ahead?

Text.SourceString: Anyway, those girls are always up to something.///<portrait=happy>Ha ha! I’d hate to miss any of it.
Text.LocalizedString: Anyway, those girls are always up to something.///<portrait=happy>Ha ha! I’d hate to miss any of it.

Text.SourceString: Big family means there's always someone around.//But it also means we never have enough milk in the fridge!
Text.LocalizedString: Big family means there's always someone around.//But it also means we never have enough milk in the fridge!

Text.SourceString: I might skip Fishensips tonight and just watch some TV at home.
Text.LocalizedString: I might skip Fishensips tonight and just watch some TV at home.

Text.SourceString: I don’t know… Just don’t feel like it.//<portrait=concerned>Wanna join?
Text.LocalizedString: I don’t know… Just don’t feel like it.//<portrait=concerned>Wanna join?

Text.SourceString: Does it feel like it rains more in Summer, or is it just me?
Text.LocalizedString: Does it feel like it rains more in Summer, or is it just me?

Text.SourceString: It’s raining hard outside, so I might as well keep the furnace on and get some work done.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s raining hard outside, so I might as well keep the furnace on and get some work done.

Text.SourceString: You here for business or just seeking shelter, <PlayerName>$player</>?
Text.LocalizedString: You here for business or just seeking shelter, <PlayerName>$player</>?

Text.SourceString: It can be pretty boring being inside all day…//But work is work.
Text.LocalizedString: It can be pretty boring being inside all day…//But work is work.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Rafael</> and I used to play in the mud in weather like this.//<portrait=happy>We’d get in so much trouble when Mom found out.//Ha! Good times.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Rafael</> and I used to play in the mud in weather like this.//<portrait=happy>We’d get in so much trouble when Mom found out.//Ha! Good times.

Text.SourceString: I might go to the Tavern after work and play some pool.//<portrait=happy>I hope to see you there!
Text.LocalizedString: I might go to the Tavern after work and play some pool.//<portrait=happy>I hope to see you there!

Text.SourceString: It’s good to see you here, <PlayerName>$player</>!
Text.LocalizedString: It’s good to see you here, <PlayerName>$player</>!

Text.SourceString: It’s storming really hard outside, so I might as well keep the furnace on and get some work done.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s storming really hard outside, so I might as well keep the furnace on and get some work done.

Text.SourceString: Are you looking for shelter or here on business, <PlayerName>$player</>?
Text.LocalizedString: Are you looking for shelter or here on business, <PlayerName>$player</>?

Text.SourceString: I can’t believe it’s still storming.//<portrait=concerned>I think I’ll go home soon.
Text.LocalizedString: I can’t believe it’s still storming.//<portrait=concerned>I think I’ll go home soon.

Text.SourceString: Well, I guess it is Winter.//<portrait=concerned>What else did I expect, besides getting snowed on?
Text.LocalizedString: Well, I guess it is Winter.//<portrait=concerned>What else did I expect, besides getting snowed on?

Text.SourceString: Ouch! Watch your step!
Text.LocalizedString: Ouch! Watch your step!

Text.SourceString: No worries…//<portrait=normal>With it being this cold, my toes are probably numb anyways.
Text.LocalizedString: No worries…//<portrait=normal>With it being this cold, my toes are probably numb anyways.

Text.SourceString: <PlayerName>$player</>, you’re covered in snow!
Text.LocalizedString: <PlayerName>$player</>, you’re covered in snow!

Text.SourceString: You should probably stay put for a bit, warm up some.
Text.LocalizedString: You should probably stay put for a bit, warm up some.

Text.SourceString: Ouch! Watch your step!
Text.LocalizedString: Ouch! Watch your step!

Text.SourceString: All good.//I don’t blame you. It’s hard to see in this weather.
Text.LocalizedString: All good.//I don’t blame you. It’s hard to see in this weather.

Text.SourceString: Long day today, <PlayerName>$player</>?
Text.LocalizedString: Long day today, <PlayerName>$player</>?

Text.SourceString: My arms are tired from working all day, but never too tired for a good game of pool!
Text.LocalizedString: My arms are tired from working all day, but never too tired for a good game of pool!

Text.SourceString: My left eye feels funny.//<portrait=annoyed>I think I got dust in it on my way here…
Text.LocalizedString: My left eye feels funny.//<portrait=annoyed>I think I got dust in it on my way here…

Text.SourceString: Why is it always in my left eye?//<portrait=happy>I guess it’s time for a new eye. Ha!
Text.LocalizedString: Why is it always in my left eye?//<portrait=happy>I guess it’s time for a new eye. Ha!

Text.SourceString: Today I told myself I’d just play one game of pool and then go home, but I always manage to talk myself into staying longer.
Text.LocalizedString: Today I told myself I’d just play one game of pool and then go home, but I always manage to talk myself into staying longer.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Rafael</>'s a real whiz. He knows more about crafting quality weapons than I do.//He's got skills.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Rafael</>'s a real whiz. He knows more about crafting quality weapons than I do.//He's got skills.

Text.SourceString: He's usually the one handling the final fold of the weapon too.
Text.LocalizedString: He's usually the one handling the final fold of the weapon too.

Text.SourceString: Oh, I don’t need a proper heater.//I work in front of the furnace all day.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, I don’t need a proper heater.//I work in front of the furnace all day.

Text.SourceString: Running a farm must take some serious planning. Deciding what to plant and when…
Text.LocalizedString: Running a farm must take some serious planning. Deciding what to plant and when…

Text.SourceString: Hey there! Good to see you, Farmer. What's the plan?//Me? Just stepping out for some fresh air.
Text.LocalizedString: Hey there! Good to see you, Farmer. What's the plan?//Me? Just stepping out for some fresh air.

Text.SourceString: Spending all day indoors probably isn't the healthiest habit.//<portrait=normal>What brings you here?
Text.LocalizedString: Spending all day indoors probably isn't the healthiest habit.//<portrait=normal>What brings you here?

Text.SourceString: This spot sure gets a lot of foot traffic, huh?//<portrait=annoyed>I always see <NPCName>Anne</> and <NPCName>Paul</> walking around here.
Text.LocalizedString: This spot sure gets a lot of foot traffic, huh?//<portrait=annoyed>I always see <NPCName>Anne</> and <NPCName>Paul</> walking around here.

Text.SourceString: It’s true. Their house is right over there.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s true. Their house is right over there.

Text.SourceString: So, what brought you out to this neck of the woods today, Farmer <PlayerName>$player</>?
Text.LocalizedString: So, what brought you out to this neck of the woods today, Farmer <PlayerName>$player</>?

Text.SourceString: I’m just getting out for some fresh air…and some ore.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m just getting out for some fresh air…and some ore.

Text.SourceString: It’s probably not the healthiest habit, staying indoors all day.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s probably not the healthiest habit, staying indoors all day.

Text.SourceString: [<NPCName>Pablo</> is hard at work on his speaker.]
Text.LocalizedString: [<NPCName>Pablo</> is hard at work on his speaker.]

Text.SourceString: Oh, hey! Wanna listen to something?
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, hey! Wanna listen to something?

Text.SourceString: Nice!
Text.LocalizedString: Nice!

Text.SourceString: All right. That’s cool!
Text.LocalizedString: All right. That’s cool!

Text.SourceString: Oh! Farmer <PlayerName>$player</>, hello!//What brings you here?
Text.LocalizedString: Oh! Farmer <PlayerName>$player</>, hello!//What brings you here?

Text.SourceString: Me? I like to help keep it clean.//Folks ought to respect the dead, you know?//It clears my head too!
Text.LocalizedString: Me? I like to help keep it clean.//Folks ought to respect the dead, you know?//It clears my head too!

Text.SourceString: Smell that?//Sweet Spring air! I’m so glad Winter is over. Ha ha.
Text.LocalizedString: Smell that?//Sweet Spring air! I’m so glad Winter is over. Ha ha.

Text.SourceString: The temperature outside only feels right to me in Summer.//Maybe because I’m always in front of a furnace?
Text.LocalizedString: The temperature outside only feels right to me in Summer.//Maybe because I’m always in front of a furnace?

Text.SourceString: Hey, <PlayerName>$player</>, theoretical question! What’s your dream date look like?
Text.LocalizedString: Hey, <PlayerName>$player</>, theoretical question! What’s your dream date look like?

Text.SourceString: Eh, not my thing. I don’t see the appeal of beaches, really.
Text.LocalizedString: Eh, not my thing. I don’t see the appeal of beaches, really.

Special.SourceString: A romantic walk on the beach.
Special.LocalizedString: A romantic walk on the beach.

Text.SourceString: That sounds perfect! You’ve got the right idea.
Text.LocalizedString: That sounds perfect! You’ve got the right idea.

Special.SourceString: A delicious home-cooked meal by candlelight.
Special.LocalizedString: A delicious home-cooked meal by candlelight.

Text.SourceString: Hey, not too shabby! I could go for that. Theoretically. Ha ha!
Text.LocalizedString: Hey, not too shabby! I could go for that. Theoretically. Ha ha!

Special.SourceString: A hiking trip to sleep under the stars.
Special.LocalizedString: A hiking trip to sleep under the stars.

Text.SourceString: That sounds perfect! You’ve got the right idea.
Text.LocalizedString: That sounds perfect! You’ve got the right idea.

Special.SourceString: A night at the bar with dancing and drinks.
Special.LocalizedString: A night at the bar with dancing and drinks.

Text.SourceString: So, <PlayerName>$player</>! What kind of music do you play to unwind, eh?
Text.LocalizedString: So, <PlayerName>$player</>! What kind of music do you play to unwind, eh?

Text.SourceString: Makes sense! That stuff makes me sleepy.
Text.LocalizedString: Makes sense! That stuff makes me sleepy.

Text.SourceString: Aww, yeah! Same here!//<portrait=blushing><NPCName>Rafael</> thinks it’s too much, but it helps me let loose.
Text.LocalizedString: Aww, yeah! Same here!//<portrait=blushing><NPCName>Rafael</> thinks it’s too much, but it helps me let loose.

Text.SourceString: So refined! Ha ha.
Text.LocalizedString: So refined! Ha ha.

Text.SourceString: Huh! I like both, really.//<portrait=normal>Got any recommendations?
Text.LocalizedString: Huh! I like both, really.//<portrait=normal>Got any recommendations?

Text.SourceString: Read anything interesting lately, <PlayerName>$player</>?//Tell me all about it… I like hearing you talk about the books you read.
Text.LocalizedString: Read anything interesting lately, <PlayerName>$player</>?//Tell me all about it… I like hearing you talk about the books you read.

Text.SourceString: Sometimes I come here to get away, but a guy like me rarely minds company.//<portrait=happy>Come on in!
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes I come here to get away, but a guy like me rarely minds company.//<portrait=happy>Come on in!

Text.SourceString: If anything weird ever happens on the farm, come tell me!//I love a good story.
Text.LocalizedString: If anything weird ever happens on the farm, come tell me!//I love a good story.

Text.SourceString: Have you read up on any of the local folklore?//Good stuff, whether you believe it or not.
Text.LocalizedString: Have you read up on any of the local folklore?//Good stuff, whether you believe it or not.

Text.SourceString: Me? I guess I’ve never thought about it.//<portrait=normal>I see no reason why those things couldn’t be true.
Text.LocalizedString: Me? I guess I’ve never thought about it.//<portrait=normal>I see no reason why those things couldn’t be true.

Text.SourceString: Well, isn't this a nice surprise! Always a pleasure, <PlayerName>$player</>.
Text.LocalizedString: Well, isn't this a nice surprise! Always a pleasure, <PlayerName>$player</>.

Text.SourceString: You just made my Monday much, much better.//What brought you to this side of the island?
Text.LocalizedString: You just made my Monday much, much better.//What brought you to this side of the island?

Text.SourceString: Being the oldest son in the family has its own burdens.
Text.LocalizedString: Being the oldest son in the family has its own burdens.

Text.SourceString: I have to carry on with the shop… Not disappoint the family, you know?//I feel like it isn’t an option for me not to be a blacksmith. <NpcName>Rafael</>… He can walk away whenever he wants to.
Text.LocalizedString: I have to carry on with the shop… Not disappoint the family, you know?//I feel like it isn’t an option for me not to be a blacksmith. <NpcName>Rafael</>… He can walk away whenever he wants to.

Text.SourceString: Well, sure, nobody’s forcing me. You’re right.//I guess the guilt is hard to explain.
Text.LocalizedString: Well, sure, nobody’s forcing me. You’re right.//I guess the guilt is hard to explain.

Text.SourceString: My parents keep bugging me about giving them grandkids. *sighs* Every time I see them, it’s “Where are my grandkids? Where are my grandkids?”
Text.LocalizedString: My parents keep bugging me about giving them grandkids. *sighs* Every time I see them, it’s “Where are my grandkids? Where are my grandkids?”

Text.SourceString: Well… I haven't given it much thought. But sure, why not? Maybe someday.
Text.LocalizedString: Well… I haven't given it much thought. But sure, why not? Maybe someday.

Text.SourceString: You did what?!//<portrait=normal>Oh, you went mining! I thought you said you went <Italic>lining</>, as in zip-lining or something.//I was like, “Where?”
Text.LocalizedString: You did what?!//<portrait=normal>Oh, you went mining! I thought you said you went <Italic>lining</>, as in zip-lining or something.//I was like, “Where?”

Text.SourceString: Seems like every time I turn around, you're out there, lending a hand to someone.//You're one of the good ones.
Text.LocalizedString: Seems like every time I turn around, you're out there, lending a hand to someone.//You're one of the good ones.

Text.SourceString: Do you know the mayor speaks highly of you?//And I have to say, I agree with him.
Text.LocalizedString: Do you know the mayor speaks highly of you?//And I have to say, I agree with him.

Text.SourceString: You seem tired today. Is everything all right?
Text.LocalizedString: You seem tired today. Is everything all right?

Text.SourceString: Sorry, <PlayerName>$player</>, didn't mean to pry.//Truth is, I'm feeling a bit wiped myself today.
Text.LocalizedString: Sorry, <PlayerName>$player</>, didn't mean to pry.//Truth is, I'm feeling a bit wiped myself today.

Text.SourceString: Wow, you look… Uh… Wow!
Text.LocalizedString: Wow, you look… Uh… Wow!

Text.SourceString: My bad. It's not polite to stare, I know… Just can't help myself.
Text.LocalizedString: My bad. It's not polite to stare, I know… Just can't help myself.

Text.SourceString: Hmm… I should read more books.
Text.LocalizedString: Hmm… I should read more books.

Text.SourceString: It’s just so hard to find the time, yeah? Maybe we can read together! And meet up to talk about what we’re reading.//<portrait=normal>Like a book club, but just you and me.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s just so hard to find the time, yeah? Maybe we can read together! And meet up to talk about what we’re reading.//<portrait=normal>Like a book club, but just you and me.

Text.SourceString: Hey, thanks for lending an ear. Sometimes it's nice to vent.
Text.LocalizedString: Hey, thanks for lending an ear. Sometimes it's nice to vent.

Text.SourceString: I think about my parents a lot.//They made a life for me and <NPCName>Rafael</>. Came here with nothing and made something of themselves. I feel like I owe them something.
Text.LocalizedString: I think about my parents a lot.//They made a life for me and <NPCName>Rafael</>. Came here with nothing and made something of themselves. I feel like I owe them something.

Text.SourceString: I hope they’re happy.
Text.LocalizedString: I hope they’re happy.

Text.SourceString: I like when you come and see me… You know that, right?
Text.LocalizedString: I like when you come and see me… You know that, right?

Text.SourceString: Do you swing by just to hang with me, or am I getting ahead of myself?
Text.LocalizedString: Do you swing by just to hang with me, or am I getting ahead of myself?

Text.SourceString: My family makes casseroles every Sunday.//We have our cousins over, the nieces and all.
Text.LocalizedString: My family makes casseroles every Sunday.//We have our cousins over, the nieces and all.

Text.SourceString: Usually, we watch sports or something.//Fun times!
Text.LocalizedString: Usually, we watch sports or something.//Fun times!

Text.SourceString: How are you, <PlayerName>$player</>?//Funny, I was just thinking about you this morning.
Text.LocalizedString: How are you, <PlayerName>$player</>?//Funny, I was just thinking about you this morning.

Text.SourceString: We need to hang more.//Neeeeed!
Text.LocalizedString: We need to hang more.//Neeeeed!

Text.SourceString: You have this quality. How do I say it…//You’re always so polite and warm.//I admire that in a person.
Text.LocalizedString: You have this quality. How do I say it…//You’re always so polite and warm.//I admire that in a person.

Text.SourceString: You’re the whole package, aren’t you?
Text.LocalizedString: You’re the whole package, aren’t you?

Text.SourceString: Before you take off, just thought I'd let you know, I saw some flowers over by the lighthouse.
Text.LocalizedString: Before you take off, just thought I'd let you know, I saw some flowers over by the lighthouse.

Text.SourceString: Figured you’d like that sort of thing. So, yeah…
Text.LocalizedString: Figured you’d like that sort of thing. So, yeah…

Text.SourceString: I don’t mind hard work, to be honest.//I actually kind of like it.
Text.LocalizedString: I don’t mind hard work, to be honest.//I actually kind of like it.

Text.SourceString: I couldn’t work a desk job, I don’t think.//I feel like I always have to keep moving my body to keep my mind at ease.
Text.LocalizedString: I couldn’t work a desk job, I don’t think.//I feel like I always have to keep moving my body to keep my mind at ease.

Text.SourceString: If I weren’t a blacksmith, I could certainly see myself as a farmer, to be honest.//<portrait=blushing>I spent a lot of time gardening growing up. Dirt suits me.
Text.LocalizedString: If I weren’t a blacksmith, I could certainly see myself as a farmer, to be honest.//<portrait=blushing>I spent a lot of time gardening growing up. Dirt suits me.

Text.SourceString: Well, look at you, <PlayerName>$player</>. You look fantastic.
Text.LocalizedString: Well, look at you, <PlayerName>$player</>. You look fantastic.

Text.SourceString: Wow! You look fantastic.//Where did you get that outfit?
Text.LocalizedString: Wow! You look fantastic.//Where did you get that outfit?

Text.SourceString: With everything you've got going for you... You must turn quite a few heads, huh?//You're sweet, attractive… Easy to get along with…
Text.LocalizedString: With everything you've got going for you... You must turn quite a few heads, huh?//You're sweet, attractive… Easy to get along with…

Text.SourceString: I'm not sure how I feel about that.//I just wish I could be the only one who… Forget it.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm not sure how I feel about that.//I just wish I could be the only one who… Forget it.

Text.SourceString: Ugh, I haven’t taken a proper break all week. Been working nonstop.//It’s a busy Winter for me.
Text.LocalizedString: Ugh, I haven’t taken a proper break all week. Been working nonstop.//It’s a busy Winter for me.

Text.SourceString: I’ve thought about settling down plenty of times, but it isn’t easy.//<portrait=annoyed>All these years of dating, and I’ve never met “the one.”
Text.LocalizedString: I’ve thought about settling down plenty of times, but it isn’t easy.//<portrait=annoyed>All these years of dating, and I’ve never met “the one.”

Text.SourceString: I like the idea of having someone special to go home to.//<portrait=blushing>You know, other than <NPCName>Rafael</>.//<portrait=normal>And sharing a warm bed while we grow old together seems nice.
Text.LocalizedString: I like the idea of having someone special to go home to.//<portrait=blushing>You know, other than <NPCName>Rafael</>.//<portrait=normal>And sharing a warm bed while we grow old together seems nice.

Text.SourceString: Ouch! You stepped on my foot.
Text.LocalizedString: Ouch! You stepped on my foot.

Text.SourceString: Don’t worry about it. It’s kinda dark here.
Text.LocalizedString: Don’t worry about it. It’s kinda dark here.

Text.SourceString: Being a blacksmith is kind of mundane.//Same routine day in, day out.
Text.LocalizedString: Being a blacksmith is kind of mundane.//Same routine day in, day out.

Text.SourceString: But sometimes mundane is good, eh?//I want mundane when it comes to my love life too.
Text.LocalizedString: But sometimes mundane is good, eh?//I want mundane when it comes to my love life too.

Text.SourceString: Oh! Farmer <PlayerName>$player</>, hello!//What brings you here?
Text.LocalizedString: Oh! Farmer <PlayerName>$player</>, hello!//What brings you here?

Text.SourceString: Me? Oh, you know! Just tidying up, like always.//Helping out my girls.
Text.LocalizedString: Me? Oh, you know! Just tidying up, like always.//Helping out my girls.

Text.SourceString: The view out here really is gorgeous. Just like y–//Uh, never mind.
Text.LocalizedString: The view out here really is gorgeous. Just like y–//Uh, never mind.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Luke</> and I tinker with our speakers a lot. Well, speakers, TVs, whatever’s in front of us.//<portrait=happy>Not scooters, though. Can’t do that. We don’t know <Italic>jack</> about scooters. That’s more <NPCName>Frank’s</> thing.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Luke</> and I tinker with our speakers a lot. Well, speakers, TVs, whatever’s in front of us.//<portrait=happy>Not scooters, though. Can’t do that. We don’t know <Italic>jack</> about scooters. That’s more <NPCName>Frank’s</> thing.

Text.SourceString: Been thinking about getting another tattoo, but I can't decide on what.//Any fun ideas, <PlayerName>$player</>?
Text.LocalizedString: Been thinking about getting another tattoo, but I can't decide on what.//Any fun ideas, <PlayerName>$player</>?

Text.SourceString: That…actually sounds cool!//<portrait=normal>Yeah, I might do that. Thanks!
Text.LocalizedString: That…actually sounds cool!//<portrait=normal>Yeah, I might do that. Thanks!

Text.SourceString: Ha ha! Because I’m a blacksmith?//<portrait=normal>That could work!
Text.LocalizedString: Ha ha! Because I’m a blacksmith?//<portrait=normal>That could work!

Text.SourceString: Very funny.
Text.LocalizedString: Very funny.

Text.SourceString: My parents would really like you, you know.//Want to meet them one day?
Text.LocalizedString: My parents would really like you, you know.//Want to meet them one day?

Text.SourceString: Does it feel stuffy in here to you?//<portrait=angry>We had to keep the windows shut all Winter, and now it sort of smells like…uh…soup?//What's up with that?
Text.LocalizedString: Does it feel stuffy in here to you?//<portrait=angry>We had to keep the windows shut all Winter, and now it sort of smells like…uh…soup?//What's up with that?

Text.SourceString: My brother's been talking about starting a garden, like <NpcName>Dippa</>'s.//Grow our own food.//<portrait=concerned>I don’t know...sounds like a lot. Balancing farming and blacksmithing...//I prefer to stick to one thing and do it well.
Text.LocalizedString: My brother's been talking about starting a garden, like <NpcName>Dippa</>'s.//Grow our own food.//<portrait=concerned>I don’t know...sounds like a lot. Balancing farming and blacksmithing...//I prefer to stick to one thing and do it well.

Text.SourceString: I hate to turn him down, but I think he's just got cabin fever from the Winter.//Now that it's Spring, he's all about getting outdoors, doing springtime things like gardening, cleaning up the cemetery, that sort of thing.
Text.LocalizedString: I hate to turn him down, but I think he's just got cabin fever from the Winter.//Now that it's Spring, he's all about getting outdoors, doing springtime things like gardening, cleaning up the cemetery, that sort of thing.

Text.SourceString: Whoa! Summer looks good on you. Gimme some of that glow!
Text.LocalizedString: Whoa! Summer looks good on you. Gimme some of that glow!

Text.SourceString: It’s too hot to wear anything else right now.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s too hot to wear anything else right now.

Text.SourceString: This necklace is from <NpcName>Valentina</>. She made it from shells she got at the beach.//Creative kid, isn’t she?
Text.LocalizedString: This necklace is from <NpcName>Valentina</>. She made it from shells she got at the beach.//Creative kid, isn’t she?

Text.SourceString: It was good to see you at the Harvest Festival the other day!//Wait… Was that you? Or was it just someone that looked like you?//Near the pot, with a bowl full of garlic? Yes?
Text.LocalizedString: It was good to see you at the Harvest Festival the other day!//Wait… Was that you? Or was it just someone that looked like you?//Near the pot, with a bowl full of garlic? Yes?

Text.SourceString: These boots are my favorite. Wear 'em all year round.//They’re good for walking in the snow. They have those teeth that grip your feet to the ground. Anti-slip!
Text.LocalizedString: These boots are my favorite. Wear 'em all year round.//They’re good for walking in the snow. They have those teeth that grip your feet to the ground. Anti-slip!

Text.SourceString: I miss that big, round, natural heat lamp outdoors. Spring, where are you?!
Text.LocalizedString: I miss that big, round, natural heat lamp outdoors. Spring, where are you?!
